text: hey ryan - if its still on the table + you have a chance, can you send us some info on that laptop you mentioned?
evans can take a look and see if it might be useful for what we’re doing

hey <@U13GPDA1F> , ryan is out through tomorrow, but will be back on Thursday to grab those specs. Sorry about that. It was an unexpected trip. I’ll see if we can get the info to you in the meantime, or we can bring the laptop down to our check-in on Friday
no worries! just thought I'd check in on it - super appreciate you following up, but we're moving forward either way!
how’d the Shamrock run picturing gathering go? I was one of the many 5k runners :slightly_smiling_face:
good! i haven’t spotted you in there, but we’ve got some photos to add to our sets. i’ll keep an eye out :slightly_smiling_face:
and next time hopefully ill be one of those 5K runners too :upside_down_face: currently more of a walker but working on it

Most of my photos ended up being crummy! It was cold! it made my cold worse! etc.! But i did get some useful ones (the hangup was mainly that it turned out after the fact that i was in a bad place to get the 15K runners coming in who also had the worst possible color combo on their bibs)
we’re putting together a workflow with the “Level 2” part and the Level 3 part that should let us correct/retrain more purposefully
so right now i’m in an 8 hour “i’m training a neural network” <pushes glasses up nose and waits for the cheering to subside> phase
